title: Dan Niles: Not All AI-Associated Stocks Will Win
description: Dan Niles, founder of Niles Investment Management, says not all AI-related companies will secure funding this year. He tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close” that Google-linked stocks have risen about 20% since late October, while parts of the open-AI ecosystem have fallen roughly 20%. (Source: Bloomberg)
